FBIS4-56107 "dreeu103_c_94005" FBIS-EEU-94-103 Daily Report 26 May 1994 CZECH REPUBLIC Havel Comments on Visit by Chile's Pinochet Havel Comments on Visit by Chile's Pinochet LD2605202594 Bratislava Rozhlasova Stanica Slovensko Network in Slovak 1630 GMT 26 May 94 LD2605202594 Bratislava Rozhlasova Stanica Slovensko Network in Slovak 1630 GMT 26 May 94 Slovak BFN [Excerpts] Czech President Havel is on a one-day visit to Slovakia today. [passage omitted] Commenting on the forthcoming visit by Chilean General Pinochet to the Czech Republic, Havel said: We wish to have good relations with Chile. It is a developed industrial country. However, I am not very happy about the fact that the person coming to Prague is the representative of the Chilean arms industry--Gen. Pinochet. I did not invite him, he was invited by a private company. [passage omitted]
